<Layout title="Homelab Architecture" description="A deep-dive into a self-hosted homelab running 20+ production services on commodity hardware — Proxmox, Ceph, Talos Kubernetes, Traefik, and full IaC from Terraform and Ansible.">

  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="eyebrow">Architecture · White Paper</div>
      <h1>woodhead.tech homelab infrastructure</h1>
      <p class="hero-sub">
        20+ production services on commodity x86 hardware. Fully automated with Terraform,
        Ansible, and a Makefile. Five-node Proxmox cluster with Ceph storage, Talos Kubernetes,
        and a single Traefik ingress for all traffic. Single operator.
      </p>
